@startuml
title Protocolli di comunicazione sicuri

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Operatore" as OP
rectangle "Portale Web ACME" as WEB
rectangle "API / servizi ACME" as API
rectangle "Broker MQTT ACME" as MQ
rectangle "Dispositivo veicolo" as DEV

OP --> WEB : HTTPS / TLS
WEB --> API : HTTPS / TLS
DEV --> MQ : MQTT / TLS

note right of WEB
Certificato server
Sessione protetta
end note

note right of MQ
TLS + credenziali
o certificato client
end note

@enduml